snippet.title: A Place for the Unwilling - Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1064310/A_Place_for_the_Unwilling/

A Place for the Unwilling is coming out on July 25. Wishlist on Steam to get notified once it's available.

You only have 21 days until this living city dies. The clock is ticking. You can’t be everywhere at once. Decide what to explore, who to meet and see every decision shape the curious stories and terrible secrets of this branching narrative game.
